nodes.text: Keith Hamshere was a still photographer for Star Wars Episodes I, II and III.

He also served as a still photographer for several other Lucasfilm productions, including: Indiana Jones and the Temple of Doom, Willow, The Young Indiana Jones Chronicles and Radioland Murders. Additionally, he was the cover artist for Star Wars: The Making of Episode I The Phantom Menace and for Star Wars Insider 41.
